	<div class="old"><p>&lt; <strong class="changes">==Files<br />&lt; &lt;nextversion&gt;This is an upcoming version. We are working on it! See [[ProgArm 0.2]] for current version.<br />&lt; &lt;undecided&gt;Undecided&lt;/&gt; / &lt;todo&gt;Todo&lt;/&gt; / &lt;done&gt;Done&lt;/&gt;<br />&lt; ==Improvements:<br />&lt; * &lt;done&gt;Use newer and smaller barometer (BMP180? LPS25H?) -- **DONE!** (Using LPS25H[http://www.st.com/st-web-ui/static/active/en/resource/technical/document/datasheet/DM00066332.pdf] now)<br />&lt; * &lt;undecided&gt;Smaller bluetooth module with BLE support (CC2541 with [[https://github.com/aanon4/BlueBasic BlueBasic]] or nRF51822 with [[https://github.com/pauloborges/blessed blessed]] or nRF8001)<br />&lt; * &lt;undecided&gt;Use SMD vibramotor. (But make sure that it does not get stuck)<br />&lt; * &lt;todo&gt;Reduce size to fit into 5x5cm (4x7cm currently) to reduce costs. 4x5cm would be great!<br />&lt; ** &lt;done&gt;Use combined accelgyro and magnetometer (MPU9250[http://www.invensense.com/mems/gyro/documents/PS-MPU-9250A-01.pdf])<br />&lt; ** &lt;todo&gt; Use LPS4012-222L or LPS4018-222L instead of huge inductors.<br />&lt; ** &lt;undecided&gt; Smaller transistors?<br />&lt; ** &lt;todo&gt; 0402<br />&lt; * &lt;done&gt;Charge LED is disabled when the device is turned off. This leads to false assumption that charging is not working when device is turned off by hardware switch.<br />&lt; * &lt;done&gt;**Do not use rare components!**<br />&lt; ** &lt;done&gt;Use bq24297[http://www.ti.com/lit/ds/symlink/bq24297.pdf] with LM3668[http://www.ti.com/lit/ds/symlink/lm3668.pdf] instead of LTC3566.<br />&lt; ** &lt;done&gt;bq27410[http://www.ti.com/lit/ds/symlink/bq27410-g1.pdf] instead of LTC2942.<br />&lt; * &lt;done&gt;Optional battery thermistor<br />&lt; * &lt;todo&gt;RTC supercap?<br />&lt; * &lt;todo&gt;No "mode switch"?<br />&lt; * &lt;todo&gt;Less ports, more pin headers!<br />&lt; * &lt;todo&gt;Minimalistic voltmeter. (as ProgArm extension)<br />&lt; * &lt;undecided&gt;Pulse oximetry (NJL5501R? TCRT1000? Si1141/2/3!)<br />&lt; * &lt;todo&gt;IR sensor and transmitter system. (as Ring)</strong></p></div><p><strong>to</strong></p>
